    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Ultimate Welcome to VR Shooter</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed for first-time VR players and demos to friends and family in mind, Dead Second is easy to pick up and instantly fun in short play sessions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139350/extras/c00d312e6b0a9c3741ebebbe64ce5836.poster.avif?t=1748316386\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139350/extras/c00d312e6b0a9c3741ebebbe64ce5836.webm?t=1748316386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139350/extras/c00d312e6b0a9c3741ebebbe64ce5836.mp4?t=1748316386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Depth and Competition for Endless Fun</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to learn but hard to master. Compete against the world for speed, accuracy and score across 8 missions with a huge range of guns and unlockable skins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139350/extras/6ae5f31297f6fc8ff70c8b1b7b29bc74.poster.avif?t=1748316386\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139350/extras/6ae5f31297f6fc8ff70c8b1b7b29bc74.webm?t=1748316386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139350/extras/6ae5f31297f6fc8ff70c8b1b7b29bc74.mp4?t=1748316386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become an Action Hero</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel like John Wick stringing together headshots or Neo from The Matrix dodging bullets in slow-motion. All in super smooth framerate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139350/extras/26b7302e97106e57320fcb4e68de618a.poster.avif?t=1748316386\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139350/extras/26b7302e97106e57320fcb4e68de618a.webm?t=1748316386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139350/extras/26b7302e97106e57320fcb4e68de618a.mp4?t=1748316386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arcade Style Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic shooters like House of the Dead and Time Crisis, Dead Second combines iconic lightgun-style gameplay with the next-level immersion of VR.</p>",
